## 5. Neural Networks / Deep Learning

```
1.  Artificial Neural Network  (ANN)
2.  Convolutional Neural Net   (CNN)   → Images
3.  Recurrent Neural Net       (RNN)   → Sequences
4.  Long Short-Term Memory     (LSTM)  → Time series
5.  GRU  (Gated Recurrent Unit)
6.  Transformer                        → NLP
7.  BERT                               → NLP
8.  GPT                                → Text generation
9.  GAN  (Generative Adversarial Net)  → Image generation
10. Autoencoder                        → Anomaly detection
```

---

## 6. Ensemble Methods

```
1.  Bagging      → Random Forest
2.  Boosting     → XGBoost, AdaBoost, LightGBM
3.  Stacking     → combine multiple models
4.  Voting       → majority vote of models
5.  Blending     → weighted average of models
```

