## Quick Reference — When to Use What

| Problem | Algorithm |
|---|---|
| Predict house price | Linear Regression |
| Spam detection | Naive Bayes, Logistic Regression |
| Image recognition | CNN |
| Customer segmentation | K-Means |
| Fraud detection | Isolation Forest, XGBoost |
| Recommendation | Collaborative Filtering |
| Time series | LSTM, ARIMA |
| Text classification | BERT, Naive Bayes |
| Anomaly detection | Autoencoder, DBSCAN |
| Tabular data | XGBoost, Random Forest |

